We specialize in applying numerous forestry services and treatments on the land base, including, but not limited to: 

- logging operations;
- forest road construction;
- bridge installation and removal;
- wildfire mitigation and fuel management;
- silviculture site preparation;
- site reclamation;
- forest health management and monitoring; 
- environmental monitoring;
- forest road and bridge inspections;
- wildfire suppression and protection;
- hydro, oil and gas right-of-way clearing; and
- special services for private property.

Our objective is to continue implementing safe and efficient forest management practices that will provide integrated benefits to all, and contribute to establishing a productive and prosperous future of sustainable forestry.

AFANE AFRICA est une entreprise d’exploitation forestière offrant divers services forestiers.

Nos domaines d’expertise sont :
•	L’aménagement des forêts ;
•	L’inventaire d’aménagement et d’exploitation ;
•	Le recyclage forestier ;
•	La transformation du bois,
•	La conception et la vente d’application, 
•	Le conseil, la formation et la vente de matériel forestier, 
•	Le montage et suivi des projets forestiers.
